Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Ample on-site parking with dual driveway

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE and Colliers International are pleased to market this prime industrial asset available for sale individually or as part of a combined portfolio, featuring 6 assets.

87-91 Victoria Street Smithfield represents a high quality freestanding office & warehouse facility. The property benefits from the below features:

Total Building Area: 3,700sqm*
Site Area: 5,994sqm*

• Extremely well presented modern distribution and warehouse facility
• Currently split into two tenancies with quality tenants
• Ample on-site parking with dual driveway access
• Main road, Victoria Street, exposure providing for a prominent and well sought after location
• Ideal corporate headquarters
• Two tenants providing diversification of income

Net passing income: $391,618 p.a
WALE: 3.9 years as at 1.03.2017

For a full information pack and to arrange an inspection, please contact either of the exclusively appointed agents listed.

*approx.

The site is near the intersection of the Cumberland Highway
and The Horsley Drive Smithfield. Upon this intersection are
both a prominent Shell Express (operating 24/7), Coles
Supermarket and Smithfield Tavern. The site enjoys dual
access from both the Cumberland Highway and The Horsley
Drive. The site is level, mainly clear of obstruction excluding
an abandoned building facing the Horsley Drive.

- Site Profile

A combination of two allotments – Lot 1 & Lot 2 in DP 207618.

• Lot 1 - Vacant land
  56 Smithfield Road, Smithfield
  Site area 740sqm (approximately) subject to survey
  Clear of any structure
  Access off The Cumberland Highway

• Lot 2 - former 'Smithfield Post Office'
  678 The Horsley Drive, Smithfield
  Site area 873sqm (approximately) subject to survey
  Building structure destroyed by fire
  Access off The Horsey Drive

• Zoning - B2 Local Centre (both lots)

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: High power supply via onsite substation

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
59-61 Long Street, Smithfield is a rare opportunity to secure a freestanding warehouse with high power availability and large yard for storage. Some key features include:

•	Freestanding warehouse with internal clearance from 5.2 meters to 8.3 meters
•	Access via 5 container height roller shutters – 4 located undercover awning
•	Located on Long Street with convenient access to Cumberland Hwy & close proximity to M4 Motorway
•	High power supply via onsite substation (1,200 amps) 
•	Wash bay 
•	Large concreted hardstand ideal for storage, parking or transport/logistics operators
•	Large awning providing additional undercover storage area or all weather loading / un-loading
•	Fitted out office + showroom on ground floor with amenities 

Please call joint-exclusive agents to arrange an inspection.
